{"tid":1781562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好亂買抗爭產品","createTime":"2019-12-13T08:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T14:56:43.000Z","uid":252031,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2858df3708fe07c25587639be7482537b2466eb1","tid":1781562,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/carafatchips/status/1205357916405911552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcarafatchips%2Fstatus%2F1205357916405911552&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6irXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=5b070e90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcarafatchips%2Fstatus%2F1205357916405911552&h=e8f83a17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/carafatchips/status/1205357916405911552</a><br />\n<br />\n依家市面上多咗好多抗爭產品，貼紙，公仔，iphone case⋯<br />\n但其實當中好多都係無問過design個個手足就用咗人地個設計嚟賺錢，就算你係真深黃，你會捐返d錢出嚟比612，星火，唔代表你可以侵犯知識版權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手contact下幫手design嘅手足睇下佢地嘅作品又無比人侵權啊唔該<br />\n<br />\n希望唔會有人插對黃色經濟圈要求唔好太高，尊重知識產權係好基本嘅嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef60e54e1bf090ffba3843158f8d9407835d2fd","tid":1781562,"uid":219583,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"知識產權?食得?<br />\n有咩得緊要過我買黎打卡呀"},{"pid":"c4cfee625c5ac1e88d5ca984a0fdeb39f518252d","tid":1781562,"uid":252031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5ef60e54e1bf090ffba3843158f8d9407835d2fd","tid":1781562,"uid":219583,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"知識產權?食得?<br />\n有咩得緊要過我買黎打卡呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人爭氣d得唔得"},{"pid":"e4ddbb1b917e2222b22c5a7ddaf99fe99c